snippet.title: Metroid: Dreadnought - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Command a familiar arsenal from the greatest bounty hunter in video games, dive through levelsets in coop or frag your friends in deathmatch, and discover new weapons and techniques.

Whichever you choose to do, however, one thing's for sure--Samus Aran is about to have a very, very bad day.

http://zandronum.com/forum/showthread.php?tid=4561

LEVELS (in order of appearance):
Vrack 2 - Map01
Deus Vult II - Map19
Scythe X - Map01
Scythe X - Map03
UAC Ultra - Map03
rjspace31 - Map01
Jenesis - map02
Metroid Prime: Hunters - Combat Hall
Equinox - Map09
Dissolution - Map02
ZPack - E3M3
Vanguard - Map04
The S Project - Map03
Crucified Dreams - Map05
Dark7 - Map04
ZPack - E3M5

MUSIC:
Metroid Prime - Brinstar (Gamecube DVD Demo Remix)

EXTRAS:
PresidentPeople
WaTaKiD
DrVonFungi
Eric
Marlus
TheToxicAvenger
a1337spy

(Opening Zandronum splash by Medicris)
